{"tid":1768810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大財團不是王道，撐小店才有出路。","createTime":"2019-12-04T10:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T05:36:16.000Z","uid":157911,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9841102abb7ee7b2461a57508d0ac062ba183347","tid":1768810,"uid":157911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"大型黃店已經有好多人排隊幫襯，但其實黃小店都好需要大家幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n所以我朋友整個網站 <a href=\"http://poutauzai.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpoutauzai.com&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=3284448c\" target=\"_blank\">poutauzai.com</a>  (<a href=\"http://舖頭仔.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%88%96%E9%A0%AD%E4%BB%94.com&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=08705fe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">舖頭仔.com</a>)去收集小店資料，方便大家喺一個網站就搵到小店，同時畀小店主多一個宣傳渠道！<br />\n<br />\n建立黃色經濟圈，你都可以幫到手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 登記小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U9b8GMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU9b8GMA.jpg&h=96b694db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無論你是咪店主，只要按一下網站右上角的+號，並填妥登記表格，小店便可以即時更新到網站！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 評價小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h5ivaEZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh5ivaEZ.png&h=405b7bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是黃是藍，由你決定！根據網站嘅評價系統，每間小店都可以被投選是否黃店，增加大家幫襯小店嘅信心，又減少罷錯舖嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n3. 留言支持小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwbTSTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwbTSTq.png&h=c5ead966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果想鼓勵小店，歡迎留言；幫襯過嘅更加可以留下感受畀大家參考下啦。<br />\n<br />\n4. 認證小店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZA2WQFW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZA2WQFW.png&h=b02ee8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果你是店主，可以用你的小店的email/Facebook/instagram聯絡舖頭仔。一經認證，你的小店即可獲得一個藍剔。<br />\n<br />\n4. 分享畀朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大力分享網站畀你嘅朋友，一齊撐起黃色經濟圈！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃色經濟圈，你都幫到手撐起！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f76faec65876e540379d598c21f6a246e02a4c2","tid":1768810,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"其實有無方法幫小店搬去D交通好D 多D人流既地方? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982279c754e2cb162a38fc1c04b896af704ae60d","tid":1768810,"uid":157911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:46:03.000Z","msg":"十連推 1/10"},{"pid":"117c469efd5e69d71a751e41a40f9c82e9afefb4","tid":1768810,"uid":157911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"十連推 2/10"},{"pid":"434eb0c1ec3b2ca014e8e4ae887fe64883c9b312","tid":1768810,"uid":157911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:46:30.000Z","msg":"十連推 3/10"},{"pid":"2e81f3b9dac603e2cc4cf78fecfe0ba0ec60c6d5","tid":1768810,"uid":157911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:46:43.000Z","msg":"十連推 4/10"},{"pid":"8b0fa117e3b6c44272cf8dee6cd5ca2e452499db","tid":1768810,"uid":157911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"十連推 5/10"},{"pid":"ccad3c5293b4088124d3033168bbe18684ba96c6","tid":1768810,"uid":157911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"十連推 6/10"},{"pid":"b23d73390d027b0d8debcad5e61be2ff79205d0e","tid":1768810,"uid":157911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:47